<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.1">
<l>eṅka ḷemmiṟai yempirā ṉimai yōrkku nāyaka ṉēttaṭi yavar</l>
<l>taṅkaḷ tammaṉat tuppiri yātaruḷ purivāṉ</l>
<l>poṅku taṇṇaru viputañ ceyyap poṉka ḷēcita ṟumilaṅ koḷi</l>
<l>ceṅka malamala runtiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our own god, our lord, leader of celestials, the one who grants grace</l>
<l>[And] never leaves the minds of his servants who praise [him],</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr where bloom red lotuses which brightly glitter</l>
<l>Where gold [nuggets] are sprinkled when roiling cool cascades create mist.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
